It has exceeded the target of chalking up annual sales of 10
billion yuan set for the year 2000 three years ahead of the
scheduled time, according to today's "China Daily".
</P>
<P>
The conglomerate was named to be a national high-tech
enterprise group on Friday by the State Science and Technology
Commission.
</P>
<P>
The group company has an average increase of 86 percent on
sales over the past 13 years. The stunning growth has elevated
Hai'er, which used to be a small factory, into the ranks of the
biggest electrical appliance manufacturers in China.
</P>
<P>
Creation of brand-name Haier is the most important strategy for
the group's quick development, Zhang Ruimin, chairman of the board
of Haier Group, was quoted as saying.
</P>
<P>
Haier refrigerators have stayed in the first place for 10
consecutive years in the competitions of national light industrial
products. This year's sales statistics from 35 large shops of 100
large and medium-sized cities show that Haier refrigerators, air
conditioners, and washing machines have all come first in terms of
sales volume. 
</P>
</TEXT>
