<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, December 27 (Xinhua) -- Heavy rains over the last few
days in Blora regency, Central Java, Indonesia, caused major
floods, uprooting and sending adrift two houses, inundating
hundreds of others and destroying four bridges.
</P>
